{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-component-tsx","path":"/component/Switch/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"da7c5192-3eb9-5914-b07b-f986e6b34740","excerpt":"简介 Switch 开关，常被翻译为开关、滑动开关、切换开关，作为界面中可直接操作的组件，提供两个互斥选项（如开/关、是/否、启动/禁用）供用户选择。 基本构成  开关（A） 可选文本（B） √ 可选 A.开关 操作项，允许用户将单个功能（例如个性化或显示设置）设置为活动或非活动状态 B…","html":"<!--副标题具体写法见源代码模式-->\n<h2 id=\"简介\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E7%AE%80%E4%BB%8B\" aria-label=\"简介 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>简介</h2>\n<p>Switch 开关，常被翻译为开关、滑动开关、切换开关，作为界面中可直接操作的组件，提供两个互斥选项（如开/关、是/否、启动/禁用）供用户选择。</p>\n<h2 id=\"基本构成\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E6%9E%84%E6%88%90\" aria-label=\"基本构成 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>基本构成</h2>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 236px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 58.47457627118644%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"1\"\n        title=\"1\"\n        src=\"/u-design/static/3ab2f7786aa879b102243c40f8a81b37/a7bcd/1.png\"\n        srcset=\"/u-design/static/3ab2f7786aa879b102243c40f8a81b37/a7bcd/1.png 236w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 236px) 100vw, 236px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th align=\"center\">开关（A）</th>\n<th align=\"center\">可选文本（B）</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">√</td>\n<td align=\"center\">可选</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p><strong>A.开关</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>操作项，允许用户将单个功能（例如个性化或显示设置）设置为活动或非活动状态</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>B.可选文本</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>表明开关当前所处的状态</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"基本样式\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E6%A0%B7%E5%BC%8F\" aria-label=\"基本样式 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>基本样式</h2>\n<h3 id=\"尺寸\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E5%B0%BA%E5%AF%B8\" aria-label=\"尺寸 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>尺寸</h3>\n<p>开关 <code class=\"language-text\">Switch</code> 预设了 <code class=\"language-text\">sm</code>、 <code class=\"language-text\">md</code>、<code class=\"language-text\">lg</code>三种尺寸，高度分别为00px、 28px、32px。</p>\n<p>小号开关</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 196px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 73.46938775510203%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"2\"\n        title=\"2\"\n        src=\"/u-design/static/950ee8e3fdc4b3cc589f3c3e98bfb34f/ad4c1/2.png\"\n        srcset=\"/u-design/static/950ee8e3fdc4b3cc589f3c3e98bfb34f/ad4c1/2.png 196w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 196px) 100vw, 196px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>中号开关</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 226px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 62.83185840707964%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"3\"\n        title=\"3\"\n        src=\"/u-design/static/77a132beb9fae8267ed75affd3a56332/5f7d4/3.png\"\n        srcset=\"/u-design/static/77a132beb9fae8267ed75affd3a56332/5f7d4/3.png 226w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 226px) 100vw, 226px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>大号开关</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 260px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 60%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"4\"\n        title=\"4\"\n        src=\"/u-design/static/7c98df501ba0322077a9bdee98235e95/86c28/4.png\"\n        srcset=\"/u-design/static/7c98df501ba0322077a9bdee98235e95/86c28/4.png 260w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 260px) 100vw, 260px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<h3 id=\"状态\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E7%8A%B6%E6%80%81\" aria-label=\"状态 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>状态</h3>\n<p>U-Design的 开关 <code class=\"language-text\">Switch</code> 有以下几种状态：\n关闭状态下：正常、hover、禁用\n开启状态下：正常、hover、禁用\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 396px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 350%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"5\"\n        title=\"5\"\n        src=\"/u-design/static/214859b1ea54209980a5c8b0f764335e/db910/5.png\"\n        srcset=\"/u-design/static/214859b1ea54209980a5c8b0f764335e/f21e7/5.png 360w,\n/u-design/static/214859b1ea54209980a5c8b0f764335e/db910/5.png 396w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 396px) 100vw, 396px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<h2 id=\"设计说明\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E8%AF%B4%E6%98%8E\" aria-label=\"设计说明 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>设计说明</h2>\n<h3 id=\"对色盲友好\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E5%AF%B9%E8%89%B2%E7%9B%B2%E5%8F%8B%E5%A5%BD\" aria-label=\"对色盲友好 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>对色盲友好</h3>\n<p>据调查色盲发生率在我国男性约为5%～8%、女性0.5～1%。从对色盲群体有好的角度来看，我们可以将可选文本的文案设置为“开”和“关”这样的表意。\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 212px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 106.60377358490565%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"6\"\n        title=\"6\"\n        src=\"/u-design/static/a9abdf0109c676bbe82eec5048f7aba3/9f128/6.png\"\n        srcset=\"/u-design/static/a9abdf0109c676bbe82eec5048f7aba3/9f128/6.png 212w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 212px) 100vw, 212px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<h3 id=\"标签的表述尽量使用肯定句，不用使用否定词的语句\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E6%A0%87%E7%AD%BE%E7%9A%84%E8%A1%A8%E8%BF%B0%E5%B0%BD%E9%87%8F%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E8%82%AF%E5%AE%9A%E5%8F%A5%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%8D%E7%94%A8%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E5%90%A6%E5%AE%9A%E8%AF%8D%E7%9A%84%E8%AF%AD%E5%8F%A5\" aria-label=\"标签的表述尽量使用肯定句，不用使用否定词的语句 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>标签的表述尽量使用肯定句，不用使用否定词的语句</h3>\n<p>与表单 <code class=\"language-text\">Form</code> 结合使用时，标签的表述尽量使用肯定句，例如“不为我推荐”，这个句子本身就是否定句，开关控件本身也有打开和关闭两个属性，这时为了理解此开关的含义需要绕弯理解，会误导用户，增加理解成本。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 714px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 15.555555555555555%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAADCAYAAACTWi8uAAAACXBIWXMAABYlAAAWJQFJUiTwAAAAbElEQVQI142O6wqDMAxG+/5PKGzg/gznpbjRamsu/cSCVYaDHQj5SMghRlTBLFiIct9IKeX6Zp+pJsSFESLD+Yg5UNkZP814Nh2q2wNtb/8SEivc22PsP7jXLwzWH8JfR1ecPwyBQCQ5i2gRrgSU7DpbO+CRAAAAAElFTkSuQmCC'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"7\"\n        title=\"7\"\n        src=\"/u-design/static/9cf7cb1794302df01f15c66f83a071d2/d67ca/7.png\"\n        srcset=\"/u-design/static/9cf7cb1794302df01f15c66f83a071d2/f21e7/7.png 360w,\n/u-design/static/9cf7cb1794302df01f15c66f83a071d2/d67ca/7.png 714w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 714px) 100vw, 714px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<!--\n\n## 主题\n\n| 内容 | 值           | 默认值  |\n| :--- | :----------- | :------ |\n| icon | icon/nothing | nothing |\n| icon | icon/nothing | nothing |\n\n-->\n<h2 id=\"相关文档\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E7%9B%B8%E5%85%B3%E6%96%87%E6%A1%A3\" aria-label=\"相关文档 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>相关文档</h2>\n<ol>\n<li><a href=\"/u-design/component/Checkbox/\">Checkbox 多选</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/u-design/component/Button/\">Button 按钮</a></li>\n</ol>","headings":[{"value":"简介","depth":2},{"value":"基本构成","depth":2},{"value":"基本样式","depth":2},{"value":"尺寸","depth":3},{"value":"状态","depth":3},{"value":"设计说明","depth":2},{"value":"对色盲友好","depth":3},{"value":"标签的表述尽量使用肯定句，不用使用否定词的语句","depth":3},{"value":"相关文档","depth":2}],"fields":{"slug":"/component/list/Switch/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"","description":"信息添加、录入的通用形式","order":null}}},"pageContext":{"id":"da7c5192-3eb9-5914-b07b-f986e6b34740","previousPostId":"9fc08bda-2303-57c0-b2ca-1d9a13b37d6a","nextPostId":"fe95a2f7-5f78-58ea-842d-c2f44f0b7047"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3000541721","850322689"]}